# CSCN_portal environment variables
# Copy relevant values into your shell environment before running `python main.py`.
# (This project reads these from the process environment; it does not auto-load a .env file.)

# Password for the auto-created "superadmin" account on FIRST run with an empty database.
# Left UNSET on purpose: a strong random password is generated on first run and written
# to C:\CSCN\credentials.txt (and the app log). Set this only if you want a fixed initial
# password — do NOT commit a real password here.
# CSCN_portal_SUPERADMIN_PASSWORD=

# Notes:
# - The SQLite database path is fixed at data/center_management.db (see config/settings.py).
# - Logs are written under data/logs/ (see config/logging_config.py).
